.B "7th Release - March 2004"
.BS
[040326] Release wrapped - public release tag is \fB20040301\fR for executable
and macros. 
.BU    
[040326]  Support for  \s-1MAC\s0  O/S Darwin  image.  Console  only (no build
machine available for X-11 version).
.BU
[040326] Introduction of \s-1UPX\s0 on Windows and \s-1DOS\s0  executables for
\fBne\fR only.
.BU    
[040326]  Support for  \s-1MS-DOS\s0  long name under  \s-1DJGPP\s0  v2.0. For
version 2.0 then the  \s-1DJGPP\s0  functions  must be invoked rather than the
\s-1MS-DOS\s0 \s-1BIOS\s0 calls otherwise the modified short name is returned.
\s-1DJGPP\s0 v1 is still supported original definitions maintained.
.BU
[040326] Added  
.Ht filetype 3f
macro to determine the file type of \s-1MS-DOS\s0, Windows or \s-1UNIX\s0.
.BU    
[040322] \fI$mouse\fR variables configured under console modes to allow pseudo
mouse operations to be performed.
.BU
[040322] Fixed the \fBwin32s\fR  build and emain.h  definitions. Mouse was not
supported under \fIwin32s\fR through incorrect configuration definition.
.BU
[040322] Key  bindings for the file  browser.  \fCENTER\fR  now handled on the
reserved fields to sort. \fCBACKSPACE\fR now moves up a directory level.
.BU
[040322] Changed the interface to \fBcvs\fR, \fBftp\fR and  \fBfile-browser\fR
command so that if a numeric  argument of \fC0\fR is given then the  directory
tree window is not opened, just the \fC*files*\fR buffer.
.BU
[040322] AutoIt hook. Thanks to Dr Detlef Groth.
.BU
[040322] Added CSS template. Thanks to Gabriel Tabares-Barreiro.
.BU
[040318] Fix to Microsoft Windows clipboard when operating with VNC.
.BU
[040317] Macro and source release set to "\fC20040301\fR".
.BU
[040317] Added 
.Ht find 3
command to macro set.
.BU
[040317] Corrected  
.Ht rgrep 3
to use the  
.Ht %find-com 5 
to specify the 
.Hr find 1
command.
.BU
[040310] Fix to graphical diff \-
.Ht gdiff 3 .
Occasions  where all changes had been  accepted  and the changes  could not be
saved. gdiff incorrectly prompted user to accept all changes first.
.BU
[040310]  Support for multiple  comment styles in the same language  template.
Additional comment styles are defined in the  "\fChkXXX.emf\fR"  file with the
syntax "\fC.fhook-XXX.comment-N\fR" where "\fCN\fR" is an integer starting for
\fI1\fR to \fIn\fR, the number of different  comment styles. Templates updated
to use multiple comment styles where appropriate (C, C++ and SQL).
.BU
[040310] Support the '\fIr\fR' flag in "\fC.fhook-XXX.comment\fR"  flag field.
Causes the key  binding to  "\fCesc-o\fR"  and  "\fCesc-q\fR"  to restyle  the
comment. All templates updated to include the flag where appropriate.
.BU
[040310] 
.Ht cvs 3
operates asynchronously using ipipes. Refresh problems resolved.
