.BE 0
.RS
.BS 
Point in line selected (i.e. mark == point) Hilight the line only.
.BU
Region in the line selected. Both point and mark are on the same line. Extract
the  selected  text and hilight all lines that match the search  pattern.  The
color "remove" is also pattern matched to selectively remove lines.
.BU
Region  selected  mark & point on  different  lines  Block up the region  with
appropriate hilight.
